data.value: Ink Your Story, Own Your Art

data.name: WelcomeDescription
data.value: Decorate your most precious temple with our art. We offer unique tattoos, quality, and safety with customer satisfaction as our priority. Trust us to make you happy with your new tattoo. Schedule your consultation and transform your vision into reality.

data.name: AdrianBio
data.value: I was born in Havana, Cuba, and from a young age, I was passionate about the visual arts, spending hours drawing. When I discovered tattooing, I knew I wanted to dedicate myself to this beautiful profession, starting my career in Cuba. After six years of perfecting and growing my skills, I emigrated to the United States. Here, I continue to deliver art and dedication to every client who trusts me to decorate their body, ensuring that each piece is unique and meaningful. My mission is to transform ideas into art that celebrates each person's individuality.

data.name: CommitmentDescription
data.value: At our tattoo studio, cleanliness is our top priority. We take meticulous care to ensure a pristine and hygienic environment for our clients. Your safety and satisfaction are paramount to us, and our commitment to sanitation reflects our dedication to providing the best tattoo experience possible.

data.name: OurNeedlesDescription
data.value: All tattoo needles used at InkVibes Tattoo are of the highest industry standards, pre-sterilized, and single-use.

data.name: OurInkDescription
data.value: All ink used at InkVibes Tattoo is of the highest industry standards, 100% vegan-friendly, and non-toxic.

data.name: OurProcessDescription
data.value: We adhere to the highest health and hygiene standards, assuring your safety and ours. All procedures are performed with single-use equipment.

data.name: OurSafetyDescription
data.value: All equipment and work areas used to perform procedures at InkVibes Tattoo are thoroughly sterilized and cleaned between clients, assuring you peace of mind.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Description
data.value: This privacy policy explains what data we collect and how we use it. You should read this policy to understand what kind of data we store on your device and how that information is used.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_LocalStorage_Description
data.value: Local storage (localStorage) is an HTML5 feature that allows websites to store data in the user's browser. Unlike cookies, data stored in localStorage does not have an expiration date and remains in the browser until it is manually deleted.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Usage_Title
data.value: How do we use local storage?

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Usage_Description
data.value: We use local storage to store information that improves the user's experience on our website. The information we store includes:

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Usage_Language
data.value: Selected language: We store the user's preferred language to display content in that language on future visits.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Usage_InitialView
data.value: Initial view: We store whether the user has seen the initial view to avoid showing it again.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Usage_Favorites
data.value: Favorite tattoos: We store the tattoos that the user has marked as favorites to facilitate access on future visits.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Disable_Description
data.value: You can disable local storage by adjusting the settings in your browser (consult your browser's Help to learn how to do this). Note that disabling local storage will affect the functionality of this and many other websites you visit. Disabling local storage will generally result in also disabling certain functionalities and features of this site. Therefore, it is recommended not to disable local storage.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Cloudflare_Description
data.value: We use Cloudflare CDN (Content Delivery Network) to improve the performance and security of our website. Cloudflare caches a copy of our site in multiple locations around the world, allowing users to access content more quickly from the server closest to them. Additionally, Cloudflare offers protection against DDoS attacks and other security threats.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Cloudflare_Data_Description
data.value: Cloudflare may collect information about the requests made to our website, including IP addresses, HTTP headers, and performance data. This information is used to improve the performance and security of the service. Cloudflare does not store personal data for tracking or marketing purposes.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Rights_Description
data.value: Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal data, including:

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Rights_Access
data.value: Right to access the personal data we store about you.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Rights_Correction
data.value: Right to request correction of inaccurate or incomplete personal data.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Rights_Deletion
data.value: Right to request deletion of your personal data.

data.name: PrivacyPolicy_Rights_Object
data.value: Right to object to the processing of your personal data.

data.name: CookieConsent_Message
